<br>
With an exhasperated sigh,she crawled up onto the boat,making sure her feet were steady. She was definitally not one to have sea legs.<br>
<br>
Moving over to Alysia carefully,she looks down at the unconscious boat captain,then looked to Alysia,then to the scurrying crew of the ship. She could smell the blood of innocents faintly;to her sences,everyone around was not fully innocent. She shruggs,then looks back to the unconscious boat captain.<br>
<br>
&quot;Since this one is already out,he'll do nicely.&quot; She explained to Alysia,then reached down and took the boat captain by the collar of his tunic and pulled his limp body up to her level. She inhaled deeply of the captains odor,her nose wrinkling slightly. &quot;Not the freshest pick of the bunch,but....&quot; She smirked,then looked at Alysia. &quot;Is this going to be take out?&quot;<br>
<br>
At this point,Zelia was more interested in eating,and not playing. <p>~ If I snap,you'll be the first to go.~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udaughterofshylock.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daughter of Shylock</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 115<br> <font color=#993300>(9/6/02 4:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=377.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Food?</span><hr size=1> Alysia blinked and looked at Zelia with a sigh.<br>
